lenders.name: Marty
lenders.loan_because:
Giving money to support the entrepreneurial aspirations of the people of the world is an indescribably fantastic chance that I honestly just could not pass up. The world as it is today is all too divided and unfairly unequal. The gap in financial power between the rich and poor is shamefully large, it's bloody massive.
My real passion is empowering people to meet their potential, to gasp onto their dreams and fight through to make them a reality for themselves. I lend with Kiva because it allows me to do that for people that I would never normally meet in my day to day life.

All through my life I have done what I can to help those around me get on and do the best they can, be the best they can be. But with Kiva I can offer that very same support to people thousands of miles away and make an even bigger impact on the world. I have much higher level of influence in the poorer countries than I do in the fist world. What Kiva has given me is a gift from the gods.
lenders.occupational_info:
I work with men that have confidence issues when approaching women in dating situations. Many very sensitive and kind men find it very difficult to show their confidence and strength to women so I talk to them and get them to complete tasks that help them to unlock their deepdown insecurities around women.
I find my work very fulfilling, to see the men that I work with meet the girl of their dreams and to know that I was able to help them on the track to finding her. All too often I find that the men that come to me are absolutely stunningly lovely and kind men that women would die to be dating but they do not have the confidence to even talk to the girls that would be interested in them.

So I take great pride in helping to bring lovely people together when they alone would not have been confident enough to approach to each other.
